## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in opinion pieces. The findings are based on a selection of articles and discussions, which may not represent the full spectrum of research on this topic. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms means that the impact on human connection may change over time, necessitating ongoing research and analysis.